{"article_id":"6JhJKE6aLn8foNMj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A sharply divided Senate","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"- reflecting a deeply divided nation -","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"voted almost entirely along party lines Saturday afternoon to confirm Judge Brett Kavanaugh to the U.S. Supreme Court .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"A little more than two hours later , Kavanaugh was sworn in during a private ceremony","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"as protesters stood on the court 's steps .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Kavanaugh becomes the nation 's 114th Supreme Court justice and President Trump 's second appointment to the court ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"creating a conservative majority on the nation 's highest court for years to come .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"The Senate vote was 50-48 .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Only one Democrat , Joe Manchin of West Virginia , joined Republicans","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"in backing Kavanaugh .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"One Republican , Lisa Murkowski of Alaska , voted `` present ''","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"although she said","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"she opposed the nomination .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"One GOP senator was absent during the vote","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"because of his daughter 's wedding thousands of miles from Washington , D.C .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Speaking to reporters on Air Force One","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"as he flew to Kansas for a political rally ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"he was `` very , very , very happy '' about the vote","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Kavanaugh will be `` a brilliant Supreme Court justice for many years . ''","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"After the vote , the president called Kavanaugh","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"to congratulate him ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"the White House said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Trump also spoke with Vice President Pence , Sen. Mitch McConnell and House Speaker Paul Ryan .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Kavanaugh was sworn in by Chief Justice John Roberts and retired Justice Anthony Kennedy Saturday evening .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Roberts administered the constitutional oath","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"and Kennedy the judicial oath .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"`` Both oaths will be administered","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"so that [ Kavanaugh ] can begin to participate in the work of the Court immediately , ''","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"the court said in a statement prior to the swearing in .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"A formal investiture ceremony will take place at a later date ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"the Supreme Court also said .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"And Trump told Kansas rallygoers","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"that he will hold a ceremonial swearing-in for Kavanaugh at the White House Monday evening .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Senators sat at their desks during Saturday 's roll call ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"rising","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"when it was their turn to vote .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"The session was presided over by Pence .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"In the debate","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"preceding the vote ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"senators sounded","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"as though they were describing two different men .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"McConnell called Kavanaugh `` among the very best","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"our nation has to offer . ''","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"Sen. Chuck Grassley , R-Iowa , chairman of the Senate Judiciary Committee , called the 53-year-old Kavanaugh a victim of `` an ugly left-wing smear campaign ''","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"and charged Democrats with character assassination .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Kavanaugh had been accused by three women of sexual misconduct","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"while he was in high school and college more than 30 years ago -","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"charges","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"he angrily denied .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer , D-N.Y. , called Kavanaugh 's confirmation `` a low moment for the Senate , the court , and the country ''","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"and said of Kavanaugh ,","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"`` He does n't belong on the nation 's highest bench . ''","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"Sen. Patty Murray , D-Wash. ,","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"who was first elected in the `` Year of the Woman '' in 1992 after the confirmation of Justice Clarence Thomas ,","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"said","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"in confirming Kavanaugh","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"the Senate would be telling young girls and women","depth":15},{"id":60,"text":"that `` your voices just do n't matter . ''","depth":15},{"id":61,"text":"On Air Force One , Trump told reporters","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"his speech in Mississippi last week ,","depth":15},{"id":63,"text":"in which he was widely seen to be mocking Christine Blasey Ford ,","depth":15},{"id":64,"text":"`` had such a great impact .","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"I think","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"it was a very important thing . ''","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"Ford had accused Kavanaugh of sexually assaulting her in 1982","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"when they both were in high school .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"Trump also said","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"women ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"far from being outraged at Kavanaugh ,","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"`` were outraged at what happened to Brett Kavanaugh ,","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"outraged . ''","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"Asked about the # MeToo movement and her husband 's recent comments about its potential impact on men ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"first lady Melania Trump weighed in on Kavanaugh 's controversial nomination before Saturday 's vote .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"`` I would say","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"if we 're talking about the Supreme Court and Judge Kavanaugh ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"I think","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"he 's highly qualified for the Supreme Court , ''","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"Mrs. Trump said","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"while speaking to reporters in Egypt during a solo international trip to Africa .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"`` I 'm glad","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"that Dr. Ford was heard ;","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"I 'm glad that Judge Kavanaugh was heard .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"FBI investigation was done ,","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"is completed","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"and Senate voted . ''","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"But","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"when asked","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"whether she believed Ford ,","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"the first lady would not answer directly .","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"`` I will move on that","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"and I think","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"that all the victims , they need -","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"we need to help all the victims","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"no matter what kind of abuse they had ,","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"but I am against any kind of abuse or violence , ''","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"the first lady said .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"In the hours before the vote , police arrested demonstrators","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"who had broken through barriers around the Capitol","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"and tried to climb the building 's steps .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"Protesters were also heard shouting from the Senate gallery during the roll call .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"A total of 164 people were arrested","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"according to U.S. Capitol Police .","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"Speak","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"ng after the vote ,","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"cConnell said","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"he protests against Kavanaugh over the past several weeks have `` turned our base on fire . ''","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"iting the Democrats on the Judiciary Committee and `` the virtual mob","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"hat assaulted us in the course of this process , ''","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"cConnell said","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"` they 've managed to deliver the only thing","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"hat we had not been able to figure out how to do ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"hich was to get our folks fired up . ''","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"recent NPR/PBS NewsHour/Marist poll showed in fact","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"hat the Republicans have narrowed the enthusiasm gap with Democrats in the past few weeks .","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"n an interview with the Washington Post , Trump said","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"urkowski will face political consequences","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"or opposing Kavanaugh .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"` I think","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"he will never recover from this , ''","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"rump said .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"` I think","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"he people from Alaska will never forgive her for what she did . ''","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"urkowski lost a primary battle in 2010","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"ut was re-elected as a write-in candidate .","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"he next faces voters in 2022 .","depth":4},{"id":128,"text":"n Friday ,","depth":4},{"id":129,"text":"fter the nomination cleared a key procedural hurdle with a 51-49 vote ,","depth":5},{"id":130,"text":"wo previously undecided senators , Susan Collins , R-Maine , and Joe Manchin , D-W.Va. , announced","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"hey would support Kavanaugh .","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"hat support all but assured Republicans of the votes","depth":4},{"id":133,"text":"hey needed","depth":5},{"id":134,"text":"o push the nomination across the finish line .","depth":5},{"id":135,"text":"n a much anticipated speech on the Senate floor Friday afternoon , Collins said","depth":6},{"id":136,"text":"hat she believed","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"hat Ford was a survivor of sexual assault .","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"till ,","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"ollins said ,","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"he allegations `` fail to meet the 'more likely than not ' standard , ''","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"nd `` I do not believe","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"hat these charges can fairly prevent Judge Kavanaugh from serving on the court . ''","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"nd in a statement","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"ssued soon after Collins spoke ,","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"anchin explained","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"e was supporting Kavanaugh","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"otwithstanding the `` serious accusations ''","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"eveled against the judge","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"nd lingering questions about Kavanaugh 's temperament .","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"` I have reservations about this vote","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"iven the serious accusations against Judge Kavanaugh and the temperament","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"e displayed in the hearing , ''","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"anchin said .","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"` And my heart goes out to anyone","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"ho has experienced any type of sexual assault in their life .","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"owever ,","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"ased on all of the information","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"have available to me ,","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"ncluding the recently completed FBI report ,","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"have found Judge Kavanaugh to be a qualified jurist","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"ho will follow the Constitution","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"nd determine cases","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"ased on the legal findings before him .","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"do hope","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"hat Judge Kavanaugh will not allow the partisan nature","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"his process took","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"o follow him onto the court . ''","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"peaking to NPR on Friday ,","depth":5},{"id":169,"text":"lawyer for Ford said","depth":6},{"id":170,"text":"he California professor 's goal was never to derail the nomination .","depth":6},{"id":171,"text":"` Dr. Ford 's goal here was never to impact the process","depth":7},{"id":172,"text":"o derail a nomination , ''","depth":7},{"id":173,"text":"ttorney Lisa Banks said on All Things Considered .","depth":6},{"id":174,"text":"` What she was trying to do was what she thought was the right thing","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"o do as a citizen ,","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"hich is to provide the information to the U.S. Senate","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"o they could make the most informed decision possible .","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"er goal was n't to derail this nomination ;","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"t was to inform the nomination","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"nd she 's done that . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":361,"left":308,"right":360,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":215,"right":307,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":195,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":187,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":185,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":183,"right":184,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":183,"left":182,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":182,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":7,"right":193,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"pare